    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家交流</h2>富婆通讯录1群：778062327<br>富婆通讯录2群：853636333<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2>这是一款魔幻现实主义的独立游戏，试图打破虚拟和现实的壁垒，在无意义、重复、枯燥和晦涩的生活中，寻找人类生命的意义。<br><br>这可能是你玩过最摸不着头脑的游戏。<br>但如果你能够坚持30天，又或者把所有NPC都无情杀掉，你将会得到跨越次元的游戏体验。当然，如果不行，那一切都只是徒劳和索然无味。<br><br>在这里，我会告诉你，你将扮演一名失业青年，在这个虚拟的世界里，活下去！但我希望你能记住，不要轻易相信我说的每一句话。<br><br>作为人类，你应当有独立思考的能力。<br>独立思考，是我创作这款游戏的初衷。<br><br>但它并不完美，因为这是我的第一款个人制作的独立游戏，用时一年零一个月。<br>在这款游戏中，它夹杂着我个人极其复杂、混乱和矛盾的思想表达。<br><br>我认为，这是不加修饰的人性。<br><br>人性本身，它应当充斥着各种复杂、混乱和矛盾情绪。<br>所以，人类追求极简、美好，以及知行合一。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2>你将扮演一名失业青年，在这个魔幻的世界里，努力生活、赚钱、吃喝玩乐，以及寻找那微不足道的真相。<br><br>买东西：以网络热梗命名的食物和书籍，主打就是一个整活。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/069b8d8dec6ccba66e1eb77a81edf7c1.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/069b8d8dec6ccba66e1eb77a81edf7c1.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/069b8d8dec6ccba66e1eb77a81edf7c1.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>打零工：偶遇100个随机事件，不同的抉择通往不同的结局。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/da3890954fe7569d558738a3bf1ac150.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/da3890954fe7569d558738a3bf1ac150.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/da3890954fe7569d558738a3bf1ac150.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>吟诗作对：以“四季+古诗词”为题材的创新小游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/9c83084753fa237664342aa41be6679c.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/9c83084753fa237664342aa41be6679c.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/9c83084753fa237664342aa41be6679c.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>大话骰：中国广东大排档宵夜KTV喝酒的必备特色玩法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/5b9513ad567d4762ff0a38761e0b6b18.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/5b9513ad567d4762ff0a38761e0b6b18.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/5b9513ad567d4762ff0a38761e0b6b18.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>股市：低买高卖，股票预测。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/87f9e3a3c346af5ee0a60c004eafb68a.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/87f9e3a3c346af5ee0a60c004eafb68a.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/87f9e3a3c346af5ee0a60c004eafb68a.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>卡牌对弈：结合“田忌赛马”和“SNAP（点数比拼）”机制的创新小游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/6ee8b7dca4858cd8ad3aed682ea1cbef.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/6ee8b7dca4858cd8ad3aed682ea1cbef.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/6ee8b7dca4858cd8ad3aed682ea1cbef.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>拍卖珍品：与NPC拍卖竞争收藏品，价高者得。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/285eff2571c0d35e8295adb274ddf148.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/285eff2571c0d35e8295adb274ddf148.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/285eff2571c0d35e8295adb274ddf148.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>鉴定古玩：以“中国神话”为题材的创新小游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/e06d8255f820d5e94a1503c13602955b.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/e06d8255f820d5e94a1503c13602955b.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/e06d8255f820d5e94a1503c13602955b.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>走马灯钢琴：结合“钢琴”和“剧情叙事”的意识流玩法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/738904c538ef5bbd8a92bc271ba74b82.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/738904c538ef5bbd8a92bc271ba74b82.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/738904c538ef5bbd8a92bc271ba74b82.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>按摩：口腹之欲，声色犬马。13名美女师傅以专业的手法带你远离消费主义的陷阱。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/9702608e7a2782add81d7950f26998d1.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/9702608e7a2782add81d7950f26998d1.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/9702608e7a2782add81d7950f26998d1.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>赛博空间：以问答的形式来探究人世间的各种问题，剧情叙事的关键入口。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/035583ff525ffce3912372185d1f568d.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/035583ff525ffce3912372185d1f568d.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/035583ff525ffce3912372185d1f568d.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>五行置换：以“五行八卦”作为题材的数值交换玩法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/2f43a3715565f5e313b3aff19dea9e9d.poster.avif?t=1741958714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/2f43a3715565f5e313b3aff19dea9e9d.webm?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353320/extras/2f43a3715565f5e313b3aff19dea9e9d.mp4?t=1741958714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>此外，你还可以跟NPC进行简单的交互，比如：蹭吃蹭喝、喝酒、借钱、睡觉。另外，你还会遇到神秘的信号，连接在现实世界中的真人视频。<br><br>如果有幸，你发现了这个世界的真相。<br>请务必在评论区告诉我。<br><br>愿人类，荣光永存！",
